'''A Guide to Middle-Earth 2004 Calendar''' was produced by Andrews McMeel Publishing and is in conjunction with the book by [[Robert Foster]]. The calendar contains information about the characters and events combined with daily entries that provide insight into the details of [[Middle-earth]].

* Dimensions: 5.5 x 5.5 inches
* Shrink-wrapped; box
